                <p> I have years of experience dealing with and helping clients. Ensuring my customers are happy, and provided with outstanding service is something I have built my reputation on. As I transitioned into the web development world, I realized that my passion for code mixed with my years of experience in customer service could help me thrive in a niche market. <h4>I often feel like a special translator for customers and code; speaking two different languages but enabling them to work together cohesively and effectively.</h4> 
